{
  "id": "RAW_576b16",
  "title": "Taro on Harmony：揭秘京东鸿蒙版如何做到\"原生级\"性能体验",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&mid=2247500756&idx=1&sn=e3b7ea4c5bc9d7729e0a861e06dd3f2b",
  "date": "2025-06-05 11:35:00",
  "author": "京东零售Taro团队",
  "siteName": "京东技术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h1 style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:500;font-size:22px;text-decoration-thickness:initial;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;line-height:1.6em;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;user-select:text;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><a target=\"_blank\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);cursor:default;padding:0px;margin:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;visibility:visible;text-decoration:none;-webkit-user-drag:none;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/appmsgalbum?__biz=MzUyMDAxMjQ3Ng==&amp;action=getalbum&amp;album_id=3813964942122745856#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"你已选中了添加链接的内容\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d1ae749-8744-4e9e-c97c-3a0117c5a200/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;vertical-align: bottom;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;height: auto !important;width: 676.992px !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/RQv8vncPm1VGIowNzKq9Hf9LD0xJmCPWgFpiaViasQCs1zJPHEt1kVAEXSWXDnycKVoM1Q6J3bQmsGFM5fOpKLlg/0?wx_fmt=gif&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"87\" data-imgfileid=\"100016752\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0d1ae749-8744-4e9e-c97c-3a0117c5a200/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></a></span></h1>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" mpa-font-style=\"mbitoeaw1e6l\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;margin-top: 0px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbitoebu8oe\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;\">纯血鸿蒙逐渐成为全球第三大操作系统，业界也掀起了适配鸿蒙原生的浪潮，用户迁移趋势明显，京东作为国民应用，为鸿蒙用户提供完整的购物体验至关重要。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">去年 9 月，京东 APP 纯血鸿蒙 在鸿蒙应用商城正式上线，APP 中核心购物链路，如首页、搜索、商详、购物车、订单、结算和我京等页面，都是通过 Taro on Harmony 方案进行开发，并且一上线就获得了华为的 S 级应用认证。</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Taro鸿蒙方案支持开发者使用React DSL来快速开发高性能原生鸿蒙应用，让 Taro具备了</span></span><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">一份代码同时跨鸿蒙、小程序、H5、React Native 多端的能力</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">，同时Taro支持类Web的开发范式，可以让开发者以熟悉的方式来开发鸿蒙应用，大幅</span></span><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">降低鸿蒙开发门槛</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">，并且存量的Taro业务也能快速转成鸿蒙原生应用，节约大量研发成本。</span></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.6em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:none;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">该方案基于鸿蒙CAPI进行构建，实现了将React DSL直接对接到C++侧来运行整体渲染管线，从而实现了与原生齐平的渲染性能，</span></span><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;outline:0px;max-width:100%;text-indent:0em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">在应用渲染性能、操作响应时延上都做到业界极致。</span></strong></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:1px;display:inline !important;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c378057c-1cc6-46af-b5c6-05a3b364f100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.2138888888888888\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"702\" data-imgfileid=\"100029113\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c378057c-1cc6-46af-b5c6-05a3b364f100/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <section style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <section style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">01</span></strong>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Taro 介绍</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Taro 是由京东发起并维护的开放式跨端跨框架解决方案，支持以 Web 的开发范式来实现小程序、H5、原生 APP 的跨端统一开发，从 18 年开源至今，在 GitHub 已累计获得 36,000+ Stars。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b1e74d0e-ba1e-48ed-5834-691b1e2d8a00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.46944444444444444\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"271\" data-imgfileid=\"100029096\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b1e74d0e-ba1e-48ed-5834-691b1e2d8a00/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在过去的一年中，Taro 完成了鸿蒙适配方案的开发，Taro on Harmony 方案支持开发者使用 React DSL 来快速开发高性能原生鸿蒙应用，让 Taro 具备了一份代码同时跨鸿蒙、小程序、H5、React Native 多端的能力，可以让开发者以熟悉的方式来开发鸿蒙应用，大幅降低鸿蒙开发门槛，并且存量的 Taro 业务也能快速转成鸿蒙原生应用，可以节约大量研发成本。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <section style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <section style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">02</span></strong>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Taro on Harmony 适配方案的演进</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:1.6em;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mbitrytk1ivk\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbitryuk1wob\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 ArkTS 的初始版本</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Taro 适配鸿蒙方案经过了多个版本的演进迭代，最初版本我们采用的是对接到鸿蒙原生 ArkTS 语言的方式来实现，这和 Taro 适配微信小程序的方案类似，都是通过模拟浏览器 DOM/BOM 环境，然后运行 React 代码构建出虚拟 DOM 树，再将虚拟 DOM 树以递归遍历的方式构建出宿主环境（小程序/鸿蒙）的渲染节点树，从而实现页面渲染。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e826155-88b9-481c-c010-abbfc1423000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.41759259259259257\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"242\" data-imgfileid=\"100029097\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e826155-88b9-481c-c010-abbfc1423000/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">但这个方案的缺陷非常明显，那就是在 ArkTS 之上再桥接一层转换，导致性能相比原生存在一定差异，并且这个差异几乎没有办法可以抹平。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:1.6em;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mbitsrge14r7\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbitsrhcgve\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\">基于 C API 的全新版本</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">恰逢此时，鸿蒙为了方便三方框架与应用接入鸿蒙生态，在官方开发语言 ArkTS 之外，开放了更底层 C API 能力，提供了 C++ 层的 UI 节点创建、属性设置等能力（类似于 C++ 版本的 DOM），三方框架和应用可以基于 C API 构建高性能的解决方案和应用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfe0cf25-dcfc-42d8-461d-9aa3e0313100/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6064453125\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1024\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"351\" data-imgfileid=\"100029099\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/bfe0cf25-dcfc-42d8-461d-9aa3e0313100/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">C API 就是 Taro 想要的能力，与 Taro 的架构完美契合，Taro React 构建出来的虚拟 DOM 树可以通过 C API 直接去创建原生 UI 节点，省去了很多流程环节，并且可以将我们大部分的渲染管线处理沉到 C++ 中去，获得飞跃式的性能提升，所以基于 C API 我们首先设计并开发了单线程架构版本。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">单线程架构版本</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">单线程架构版本的示意图如下，整个渲染过程均在主线程实现，业务代码在 ArkVM 中执行获得虚拟 DOM 树，同时读取样式数据，通过 React Reconciler ，在构建虚拟树时会调用 NAPI 在 C++ 侧构建出对应的 Element Tree，同时也会进行样式数据的解析处理，从而构建出 CSSOM 对象，Element Tree 和 CSSOM 对象会进行匹配从而构建出带有样式的 Render Tree，在这一步也会同时创建 yoga 节点，进行布局计算，最后会再基于布局计算的结果生成 C API 的 ArkNode Tree，从而实现上屏渲染。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0a5ac34-759c-48da-657a-2042fc0c1900/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.41388888888888886\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"239\" data-imgfileid=\"100029100\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0a5ac34-759c-48da-657a-2042fc0c1900/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">目前京东鸿蒙 APP 中首页、搜推、我京、核心购物流程均是使用 Taro 单线程版本进行开发，性能和稳定性位于第一梯队。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0dc3f368-70d8-4f06-803c-2648e9bace00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"325\" data-imgfileid=\"100029102\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/0dc3f368-70d8-4f06-803c-2648e9bace00/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">多线程架构版本</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">单线程版本上线之后，我们也发现了单线程架构的不足，① 从业务代码的执行到渲染流程的处理都发生在主线程上，这导致了主线程的过载，使得应用无法及时响应用户的操作，从而引发了用户体验上的卡顿，随着业务逻辑的增加和复杂性的提升，这种卡顿现象会越发明显；② 在单线程架构下，代码都是需要内置到应用包里，这样就无法实现业务代码的动态下发更新。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">所以，为了解决以上问题，进一步提升应用性能，和应对未来更多业务场景需求的可能性，我们实现了多线程架构。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/844cc56f-a955-4043-42f8-33379512e500/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.5398148148148149\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"312\" data-imgfileid=\"100029104\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/844cc56f-a955-4043-42f8-33379512e500/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">相较于单线程架构，多线程架构将整个业务代码执行和渲染的过程拆分到了三个线程，每个线程各司其职，让任务的执行更加合理，不会造成主线程的堵塞，这样的架构主要带来三个好处。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">1.业务逻辑不再堵塞主流程，完全剥离到了单独的线程执行，之前容易出现卡顿、甚至 APP Freeze 的页面基本不再有问题，例如商详接入之后滑动页面变得更加流畅；</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">2.动画执行和渲染不再卡顿，动画的执行交由 Background 线程管控，不再和 JS 线程有冲突问题，动画支持满帧渲染；</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">3.支持动态化的能力，在性能上可以与原生相媲美，同时还能支持动态下发，支持更新远端 JS 资源来实现 APP 内容的更新，让业务具备快速验证和免发版的能力。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">目前多线程版本正在我们的业务中进行试点接入，很快就会正式上线。&nbsp;</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <section style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <section style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">03</span></strong>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Taro on Harmony 方案特性</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:1.6em;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mbittjlycpe\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbittjmx1bse\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\">丰富的能力支持</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">常用组件和 API 支持</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在 C-API 版本的 Taro For Harmony 中，我们不仅完整支持了 React 18+，另外支持了 View、Text、Image、Video 等近 33 个 Taro 组件，对于常用的 API，如 getSystemInfo、getStorage 等也是在 C-API 版本中得到了完整的支持，而且针对逻辑较为复杂的 API 如：createSelectorQuery 以及 createIntersectionObserver，我们将这些 API 在 C++ 侧进行了重新的实现，大幅提升了他们的执行性能。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">常用样式支持</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在 C-API 版本中，我们对支持了大部分常见的 CSS 能力：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持常见的 CSS 样式和布局，支持 flex、伪类和伪元素</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持常见的 CSS 定位，绝对定位、fixed 定位</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持常见的 CSS 选择器和媒体查询</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持常见的 CSS 单位，比如 vh、vw 以及计算属性 calc</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">支持 CSS 变量以及安全区域等预定义变量</span></span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">同时，我们参考浏览器 CSSOM 的实现方式，在 C++ 实现了一套 CSSOM 逻辑，里面包含了样式解析、样式匹配、样式合成和应用整个链路的样式处理逻辑。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/243db088-6923-452a-d2f8-29259549ae00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"1.012006861063465\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"583\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"585\" data-imgfileid=\"100029105\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/243db088-6923-452a-d2f8-29259549ae00/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">另外，Taro 引入了 Yoga 布局引擎来计算渲染节点的位置和大小，最大程度保证 Taro 构建出来的鸿蒙应用中渲染样式和 W3C 规范的一致性。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f90da2c0-ca3b-4815-d0b0-bf2af8145400/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.30925925925925923\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"179\" data-imgfileid=\"100029106\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f90da2c0-ca3b-4815-d0b0-bf2af8145400/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;line-height:1.6em;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mbitu88t101y\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbitu89tj09\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\">媲美原生 ArkTS 的高性能</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">运行时逻辑下沉至 C++</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在 C-API 的版本中，我们将 ArkVM 层的 Taro 运行时内容削减到极致的薄，将 TaroElement 的大部分内容都下沉到了 C++ 侧，并在 ArkVM 层取消了他们之间父子关系的绑定，极大地提升了 TaroElement 相关逻辑的性能。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c2780f1-63b1-4777-5eeb-98709ae7bf00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.46296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"268\" data-imgfileid=\"100029107\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8c2780f1-63b1-4777-5eeb-98709ae7bf00/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">另一方面，在 C++ 侧 Taro 会指令式地调用 ArkUI 在 C++ 侧提供的 API，来高效地创建节点、设置属性、绑定事件以及绘制上屏。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">提供长列表组件应对长列表场景</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Taro 还针对长列表场景针对性地提供了长列表类型组件，并对长列表类型组件进行了优化，提供了懒加载、预加载和节点复用等功能，有效地解决大数据量下的性能问题，提高应用的流畅度和用户体验。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0d35ba1-60ba-4937-e9c4-aa3320c33000/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.4351851851851852\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"251\" data-imgfileid=\"100029109\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f0d35ba1-60ba-4937-e9c4-aa3320c33000/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(0, 0, 0);margin:0px 8px 24px;outline:0px;text-size-adjust:inherit;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:16px;font-family:Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;text-align:left;\" mpa-font-style=\"mbitul1blf3\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mbitul2a15g2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"outline:0px;font-weight:bolder;border-left:5px solid rgb(14, 136, 235);padding-left:10px;display:inline-block;font-family:&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持 C API 混合原生的渲染模式</span></span></h3>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Taro 的组件和 API 是以小程序作为基准来进行设计的，因此在实际的鸿蒙应用开发过程中，会出现部分所需的组件和 API 在 Taro 中不存在的情况，因为针对这种情况，在 C-API 版本中，Taro 提供了原生混合开发的能力，支持将原生页面或者原生组件混合编译到 Taro 鸿蒙项目中，支持 Taro 组件和鸿蒙原生组件在页面上的混合使用。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf72c0cb-ddb8-438c-9bd0-70857c316f00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.6212962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"359\" data-imgfileid=\"100029111\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cf72c0cb-ddb8-438c-9bd0-70857c316f00/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 24px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;justify-content: center;\">\n    <section style=\"transform-style: preserve-3d;\">\n     <section style=\"transform:translateZ(5px);letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:48px;font-style:oblique;text-align:center;\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">04</span></strong>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"margin-top: -35px;display: flex;justify-content: center;align-items: center;transform: translateZ(10px);\">\n      <strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></strong>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span leaf=\"\">总结</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n       <span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">Taro 鸿蒙方案基于鸿蒙 CAPI 进行构建，实现了将 React DSL 直接对接到 C++ 侧来运行整体渲染管线，从而实现了与原生齐平的渲染性能，同时 Taro 鸿蒙方案是多线程架构的方案，在应用渲染性能、操作响应时延上都在业界做到极致，并且 Taro 鸿蒙方案支持动态更新，是行业首创且经过大规模 APP 应用场景验证的开发框架，综合性能、生态以及开发体验来讲，毫无疑问已经成为了开发鸿蒙应用的最佳框架选型之一。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">目前，我们也仍然在不断完善着鸿蒙的适配方案，目前在渲染性能提升方面我们正在进行 React C++ 化的探索，整体进展也已经处于验证和测试阶段，同时也在进行自研布局引擎的探索，在进一步提升渲染性能的同时，为业务提供更丰富的样式写法支持；此外，在开发效率提升方面，我们也正在进行开发调试工具的探索开发，为业务提供热重载、源码定位、断点调试、元素审查等能力，提升效率和开发体验。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.6em;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;\">在近期，我们会将已经在京东鸿蒙 APP 久经考验的单线程架构版本开源出来，为开源社区贡献一份力量，为鸿蒙应用生态的丰富注入强大的动力。</span></span>\n   <section>\n    <section data-mpa-action-id=\"mb6hoooa4z6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n     <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:16px 0px 8px;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:0px;max-width:100%;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;text-decoration: none;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 2px;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">推荐阅读</span></span></strong></span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&amp;mid=2247500737&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=b9a7a5ecfaaf313b389637d0b59902dc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"EMNLP 2024 | 突破RQ-SID&quot;沙漏&quot;瓶颈，提高生成式搜推上限\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">EMNLP 2024 | 突破RQ-SID\"沙漏\"瓶颈，提高生成式搜推上限</span></a></span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&amp;mid=2247500727&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=898b174022e0fcd7911be6091ad163e8&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"在京东做AI的95后：我们这样搞定技术难题\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">在京东做AI的95后：我们这样搞定技术难题</span></a></span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&amp;mid=2247500712&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=61aeffc6f686af13a36bdc71dd042ae5&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"研发排查问题的利器：一款方法调用栈跟踪工具\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">研发排查问题的利器：一款方法调用栈跟踪工具</span></a></span></p>\n     <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;letter-spacing:0.578px;clear:both;font-size:14px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.6em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;max-width:100%;font-family:mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mb6hoon727r\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==&amp;mid=2247500628&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1247b2316f831fe1b74365e001572a13&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"行业SOTA，京东首个自研十亿级时序大模型揭秘\" data-itemshowtype=\"11\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"text-decoration:underline;\">行业SOTA，京东首个自研十亿级时序大模型揭秘</span></a></span></p>\n    </section>\n    <section data-id=\"132495\">\n     <section style=\"margin: 10px auto;display: flex;flex-direction: column;\">\n      <section style=\"display: flex;align-items: center;justify-content: center;margin: 0 0 -15px;z-index: 9;\">\n       <section style=\"background-color: #e1251b;display: flex;align-items: center;z-index: 9;\">\n        <section style=\"width: 8px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewbox=\"0 0 17.438 15.062\" style=\"display: block;\" data-height=\"100%\" xml:space=\"default\">\n          <path style=\"fill: #ffffff;fill-rule: evenodd;\" d=\"M225.359,752.466l4.36,7.532-4.36,7.532h-8.718L212.281,760l4.36-7.532h8.718Z\" transform=\"translate(-212.281 -752.469)\"></path>\n         </svg>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"padding:1px 10px;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n         <strong data-brushtype=\"text\"><span leaf=\"\">关注我们</span></strong>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"width: 8px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n         <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewbox=\"0 0 17.438 15.062\" style=\"display: block;\" data-height=\"100%\" xml:space=\"default\">\n          <path style=\"fill: #ffffff;fill-rule: evenodd;\" d=\"M225.359,752.466l4.36,7.532-4.36,7.532h-8.718L212.281,760l4.36-7.532h8.718Z\" transform=\"translate(-212.281 -752.469)\"></path>\n         </svg>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"border-radius:9px;padding:30px 10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n       <section class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n        <mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"京东技术\" data-alias=\"jingdongjishu\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/RQv8vncPm1X5Gac5XcPPmhSR2Fsq1YX7asRaOEcBOmnGFyOHNmJPRXCVx6rtfT4RiboAkQZT0IIUZdIpv8rxvBg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"京东官方技术分享平台。你想知道的京东前沿技术、创新思考、开源方案...这里应有尽有！\" data-id=\"MzU1MzE2NzIzMg==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"2\"></mp-common-profile>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "京东基于 Taro 和鸿蒙 CAPI 构建高性能跨端方案，实现原生级体验并支持动态更新。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "京东基于 Taro 和鸿蒙 CAPI 构建高性能跨端方案，实现原生级体验并支持动态更新。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了京东如何利用其开源跨端框架 Taro 适配鸿蒙操作系统，并成功应用于京东 APP 的核心购物链路。文章追溯了方案的演进，从最初基于 ArkTS 桥接的性能受限版本，升级到基于底层鸿蒙 C API 构建的全新版本。通过将渲染管线直接对接 C++层，实现了接近原生应用的渲染性能。进一步地，团队开发了多线程架构版本，将业务逻辑、渲染、动画分离，解决了单线程卡顿问题，并实现了业务代码的动态下发和免发版能力。该方案支持丰富的 React 组件、API 及 CSS 样式，引入 Yoga 布局引擎，并支持与原生 ArkTS 混合开发，目前已在京东 APP 大规模应用并验证，是业界领先的鸿蒙跨端开发框架。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "技术方案从 ArkTS 桥接到 C API 再到多线程架构持续演进",
      "explanation": "文章详细介绍了 Taro 鸿蒙方案如何从最初性能受限的 ArkTS 桥接方式，迭代到基于底层 C API 实现高性能单线程架构，最终优化至具备动态更新能力的多线程架构，展示了持续追求极致性能和灵活性的过程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Taro on Harmony 方案大幅降低鸿蒙开发门槛和成本",
      "explanation": "开发者可沿用熟悉的 React DSL 和类 Web 范式进行开发，一份代码可运行在鸿蒙、小程序、H5、React Native 等多端，存量 Taro 业务迁移快速。"
    },
    {
      "point": "基于鸿蒙 C API 实现原生级渲染性能和操作响应时延",
      "explanation": "通过将 React DSL 直接对接鸿蒙 C++侧的 UI 能力，省去中间转换层，核心渲染处理下沉到 C++，获得显著性能提升。"
    },
